    <item>
      <title>法国 30 年期债券发行需求接近创纪录水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/france-is-up-next-after-a-record-slew-of-european-bond-sales</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国公开银团债务市场今年延续了欧洲有记录以来最繁忙的开局，投资者忽略了该国的财政和政治挑战，将收益率锁定在一年多以来的最高水平附近。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/france-is-up-next-after-a-record-slew-of-european-bond-sales</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 09:55:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国行业报告显示库存大幅增加，油价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-february-12</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一份行业报告显示美国原油库存大幅增加，且市场继续关注美国总统唐纳德·特朗普的更多贸易攻势，油价随后回落。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-february-12</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 23:33:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>华尔街将迎来近一年来最糟糕的 CPI 日：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于通胀强劲，交易员将对美联储下次降息的押注推迟到 12 月，导致股市受到冲击，债券收益率飙升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 22:30:10 GMT</pubDate>
